{
  "id": "69afe340d294cf22d7f14877",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:ベルリン行動規範",
  "created": 1773134694,
  "updated": 1773134716,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69afe340d294cf22d7f14877",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:ベルリン行動規範",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134694,
      "updated": 1773134694
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3660000000000572d8e",
      "text": "[ベルリン行動規範]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134694,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572d8f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572d90",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]（進行）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572d91",
      "text": "ねえねえ二人とも～！今日のテーマなんだけどさ、「ベルリン行動規範」ってやつ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572d92",
      "text": "名前めっちゃカッコよくない？なんかラスボスのルールブック感あるんだけどｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572d93",
      "text": "とりま、これって何なのかゆるっと話してこーぜ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572d94",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572d95",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572d96",
      "text": "了解。では定義から。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572d97",
      "text": "ベルリン行動規範（Berlin Code of Conduct）は、主にイベントやコミュニティでの行動ルールを示したガイドライン。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572d98",
      "text": "特にITコミュニティやカンファレンスなどでよく採用されている。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572d99",
      "text": "目的はシンプル。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572d9a",
      "text": " 1. 参加者が安心して参加できる環境を作る",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572d9b",
      "text": " 2. ハラスメントや差別を防ぐ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572d9c",
      "text": " 3. トラブルが起きたときの対応を明確にする",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572d9d",
      "text": "公式サイト：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572d9e",
      "text": "https://berlincodeofconduct.org",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572d9f",
      "text": "要するに、コミュニティの安全設計ドキュメントだね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572da0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572da1",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572da2",
      "text": "あー！なるほど！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572da3",
      "text": "つまりさ、ゲームで言うと",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572da4",
      "text": "[** 「オンライン対戦のマナー規約」]みたいな感じ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572da5",
      "text": "暴言NGとか、迷惑行為BANとか、そういうやつ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572da6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572da7",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572da8",
      "text": "その例えは正しい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572da9",
      "text": "ただしベルリン行動規範はもう少し体系的。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572daa",
      "text": "例えば以下の要素が含まれる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dab",
      "text": " 尊重（Respect）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dac",
      "text": " 包摂性（Inclusivity）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dad",
      "text": " ハラスメント禁止",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dae",
      "text": " 運営への報告手順",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572daf",
      "text": "つまり単なるマナーではなく、コミュニティガバナンスの仕組み。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572db0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572db1",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572db2",
      "text": "なるほど……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572db3",
      "text": "それはまるで、皆が同じ広場に集まるときに",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572db4",
      "text": "「ここでは互いを傷つけぬようにしましょうね」と",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572db5",
      "text": "あらかじめ約束を交わすようなものですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572db6",
      "text": "人が集まる場所には、どうしても心の行き違いが生まれますもの。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572db7",
      "text": "そうした時のためのやさしい道しるべのように感じます。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572db8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572db9",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dba",
      "text": "おお～、あやの表現エモい…！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dbb",
      "text": "でもさ、ちょっと気になるんだけど。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dbc",
      "text": "わざわざこんなルール作らないとダメなの？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dbd",
      "text": "普通に仲良くすればよくない？って思っちゃうんだけどｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dbe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dbf",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dc0",
      "text": "良い疑問。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dc1",
      "text": "実はルールが明文化されていること自体に意味がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dc2",
      "text": "理由は主に3つ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dc3",
      "text": " 1. 認識のズレを減らす",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dc4",
      "text": "  「何がダメなのか」は人によって違う。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dc5",
      "text": " 2. 被害者が声を上げやすくなる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dc6",
      "text": "  ルールがあると「これは違反」と言える。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dc7",
      "text": " 3. 運営が公平に対応できる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dc8",
      "text": "  判断基準が事前に決まる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dc9",
      "text": "つまり、トラブル予防と透明性の確保。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dca",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dcb",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dcc",
      "text": "あーなるほど。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dcd",
      "text": "確かにネットでも",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dce",
      "text": "「それアウトだろ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dcf",
      "text": "「いや普通じゃね？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dd0",
      "text": "みたいなレスバ、めちゃあるしｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dd1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dd2",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dd3",
      "text": "ええ……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dd4",
      "text": "人の心はそれぞれ異なりますものね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dd5",
      "text": "ある人にとっては軽い冗談でも、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dd6",
      "text": "別の人には深い傷になることがあります。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dd7",
      "text": "そう考えると、こうした行動規範は",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dd8",
      "text": "人と人の間にそっと置かれたクッションのような存在なのかもしれません。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dd9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dda",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572ddb",
      "text": "いい表現だ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572ddc",
      "text": "ちなみにベルリン行動規範は",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572ddd",
      "text": "オープンソースコミュニティでもよく使われる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dde",
      "text": "例えば",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572ddf",
      "text": " 開発者イベント",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572de0",
      "text": " 技術カンファレンス",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572de1",
      "text": " ハッカソン",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572de2",
      "text": "など。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572de3",
      "text": "技術コミュニティは世界中の人が集まるから、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572de4",
      "text": "文化の違いによる摩擦が起きやすい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572de5",
      "text": "だから共通ルールが必要になる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572de6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572de7",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572de8",
      "text": "あー！グローバル鯖みたいな感じか！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572de9",
      "text": "国ごとにマナー違うもんね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dea",
      "text": "FPSとかでも",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572deb",
      "text": "「煽りは文化」みたいな国もあれば",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dec",
      "text": "「それ失礼だろ」ってなる国もあるし。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572ded",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dee",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572def",
      "text": "まさにそれ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572df0",
      "text": "ベルリン行動規範は",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572df1",
      "text": "文化差を超える最低限のルールとして設計されている。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572df2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572df3",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572df4",
      "text": "世界のさまざまな人々が",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572df5",
      "text": "同じ机を囲んで話し合うようなものですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572df6",
      "text": "そのときに",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572df7",
      "text": "「どうぞ、あなたの言葉を聞かせてください」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572df8",
      "text": "と互いに尊重できる空気があると、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572df9",
      "text": "きっと素敵な時間になるのでしょう。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dfa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dfb",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dfc",
      "text": "なんかさー",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dfd",
      "text": "最初は「お堅いルール」って感じだったけど",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dfe",
      "text": "話聞くと",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572dff",
      "text": "みんなで楽しくやるための設定ファイル",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e00",
      "text": "みたいな感じだね！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e01",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e02",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e03",
      "text": "いいまとめ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e04",
      "text": "コミュニティはシステムに似ている。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e05",
      "text": "バグを減らすには",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e06",
      "text": "ルールとプロトコルが必要。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e07",
      "text": "ベルリン行動規範は",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e08",
      "text": "いわば社会のエラーハンドリング。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e09",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e0a",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e0b",
      "text": "出た、りかの中二エンジニア語録ｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e0c",
      "text": "でもちょっとかっこいいの悔しいｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e0d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e0e",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e0f",
      "text": "皆が安心して言葉を交わせる場所があるのは、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e10",
      "text": "とても大切なことですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e11",
      "text": "図書館でも、学校でも、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e12",
      "text": "そしてインターネットでも。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e13",
      "text": "静かに守られている約束ごとがあるからこそ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e14",
      "text": "人はのびのびと語れるのかもしれません。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e15",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e16",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]（まとめ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e17",
      "text": "よし！今日のまとめいくよー！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e18",
      "text": "ベルリン行動規範とは！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e19",
      "text": " イベントやコミュニティの行動ルール",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e1a",
      "text": " ハラスメントや差別を防ぐ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e1b",
      "text": " 安心して参加できる空間を作る",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e1c",
      "text": " 世界中の人が集まる場で特に大事",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e1d",
      "text": "つまり！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e1e",
      "text": "[**** 「みんなで気持ちよく遊ぶためのルールブック」] って感じ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e1f",
      "text": "ITイベントとかでよく使われてるらしいから、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e20",
      "text": "もし将来ハッカソンとか行く人はチェックしてみてね！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e21",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e22",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e23",
      "text": "以上。議論ログ、正常終了。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e24",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e25",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e26",
      "text": "今日はとても穏やかな学びの時間でしたね。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3670000000000572e27",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134695,
      "updated": 1773134695
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3720000000000572e28",
      "text": "#2026-03-10",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134706,
      "updated": 1773134716
    },
    {
      "id": "69afe3730000000000572e29",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773134708,
      "updated": 1773134708
    }
  ]
}